lwp
------------------------------------------
Coroutine-based lightweight process package

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.8.2-1
  liblwp-devel-2.8-1bl1
  liblwp2-2.8-1bl1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-4
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-5.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-4
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.coda.cs.cmu.edu/

Canonical download:
  http://www.coda.cs.cmu.edu/pub/lwp/src/lwp-2.8.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack lwp-2.8-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./lwp-2.8-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lwp-2.8-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/lwp-2.8-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblwp2-2.8-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblwp-devel-2.8-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(lwp)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/lwp.README
  /usr/share/doc/lwp/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/lwp/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/lwp/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/lwp/PORTING
  /usr/share/doc/lwp/README

(liblwp2)
  /usr/bin/cyglwp-2.dll
  /usr/bin/cyglwp_pt-2.dll

(liblwp-devel)
  /usr/include/lwp/lock.h
  /usr/include/lwp/lwp.h
  /usr/include/lwp/timer.h
  /usr/lib/liblwp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/liblwp_pt.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/lwp.pc

------------------

